This tool depends on the `mercs2_formats` crate from the Mercenaries-Fan-Build
`mercs2-wad-simulator` project:

    https://github.com/Mercenaries-Fan-Build/mercs2-wad-simulator

`mercs2_formats` is referenced as a Cargo git dependency — its source is fetched
by cargo at build time and is NOT redistributed in this repository. It is used
with the maintainers' permission. The reverse-engineering of the Mercenaries 2
WAD / UCFX / SGES / ASET formats that this tool builds on is their work; please
credit that project accordingly.
